name: 03-Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
content:
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

Data Profiling:

  • Summary statistics for audit, financial, and loss scores.
  • Distribution of risk (0 = Safe, 1 = Risky) across locations.

Descriptive Analysis:

  • City-Wise BTS Distribution: Number of deployments per city.
  • Score Comparisons: Average financial and audit scores for risky vs. safe deployments.
  • Correlation Analysis: Relationships among audit, financial, and loss scores.
  • Risk Trends: Identifying cities consistently associated with high-risk deployments.

Visualizations:

  • Histograms of audit, financial, and loss scores.
  • Risk heatmaps showing risky deployments by region.
  • Bar plots of top high-risk vs. low-risk cities.
